description: A drink from the post-tiki era that has found great popularity coast to coast in cocktails of all stripes. Adapted by Smuggler's Cove.
source: Smuggler's Cove by Martin Cate with Rebecca Cate
author: Kuala Lumpur Hilton, circa 1978
