---

Add all the ingredients to a drink mixer in. Combine @black blended rum{1 1/2%oz}, @pineapple juice{1 1/2%oz}, @fresh lime juice{3/4%oz}, @SC Demerara Syrup{1/2%oz}, and @Campari{3/4%oz}.

Add 12 ounces of crushed ice and 4 to 6 small "agitator" cubes.

Flash blend and open pour into a #double rocks glass{} or #highball glass{}.

Garnish with @pineapple fronds{}.
